        Menu Visibility by Role:
        - User (group_eo_cfp_user): Planning menu, Reports menu, basic items
        - Manager (group_eo_cfp_manager): + Recurring Items, Forecast, Configuration
        - Director (group_eo_cfp_director): + Budgets, Budget Analysis, Alerts

        Because of implied_ids in security groups:
        - Directors see everything (they have Manager and User groups)
